{
  "texts": [
    "To automatically evaluate the quality of the generated text, we have considered BLEU-4 (Papineni et al., 2002), F1 (i.e.",
    "unigram overlap), and ROUGE-L (Lin, 2004).",
    "Furthermore, we have used KF1 (Shuster et al., 2021) to measure the overlap between the prediction and the knowledge selected \"You are presented with a user's Question about a movie or book.",
    "Answer to the user's Question using the information provided in the Context.\"",
    "\"Answer to the user's question using the provided information (if available).\""
  ]
}